{"tid":1219610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)調景嶺站有5隻警犬standby..","createTime":"2019-06-13T23:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:39:28.000Z","uid":86545,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8534dac772bd42da880e64ab1c825b56647514","tid":1219610,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60n4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60n4t.jpg&h=dfbd78e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連攝影師都係度"},{"pid":"3bf0f97de9bf75ceecf1cd269aa2ce6a90eefae8","tid":1219610,"uid":73293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:47:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊呼籲香港KOL清晰表明立場去發聲！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>急！！需要大家幫手！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"},{"pid":"c6ca3f189ae33173335c3cf8882d4f4aa86a562c","tid":1219610,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:48:49.000Z","msg":"有線啲記者走黎走去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea93c69110f60dae2cd3d1d7b1144e59cb13805d","tid":1219610,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:51:18.000Z","msg":"係咪唔翻工即係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so